From e9d0ad04cd6fe9520b8a278b85730ba8e3cb741c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Wayne <mrwayne-dev@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sun, 7 Jun 2026 19:41:20 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: rebuild user + admin dashboards for QBX cold wallet
 platform

- Sidebar: dark green gradient, 14-item QBX nav with dropdowns, mobile dock
- User dashboard: 14 sections (overview, send, receive, swap, mining, QFS card,
  investments, connect wallet, profile, KYC, notifications, security, 2FA, support)
- Dashboard CSS: 1100+ lines of new component styles + responsive breakpoints
- User JS: 14 section loaders, 6 form handlers, crypto portfolio rendering
- Database: 25 tables replacing banking schema with crypto wallet tables,
  29 assets seeded, fee schedule, system settings
- User API: dashboard stats, multi-asset wallets, send/swap with tier-based fees,
  profile/KYC/password management, CoinGecko price refresh
- Admin dashboard: 9 sections (overview, users, KYC approvals, transactions,
  virtual cards, user wallets, support tickets, mining, settings)
- Admin API: 9 GET section handlers, 7 POST actions (KYC approve/reject,
  card activation, credit/debit, ticket management, system settings)
- Admin JS: 9 loaders, search/filter/pagination, admin action prompts
